patthana23.11:1.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naparittaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca abyākato paritto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.11:1.1_1: (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā pañca, adhipatiyā pañca …pe… aññamaññe tīṇi …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana23.11:2.1_0: Nakusalaṁ namahaggataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca abyākato mahaggato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.11:3.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naappamāṇaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā kusalo appamāṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.11:3.1_1: (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha …pe… āsevane tīṇi …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
